BB Mazda Polokwane Sales Executive Fish Mamabolo congratulates Herbert Phahlamohlaka, the first customer to buy one of the recently launched Next-Generation Mazda 3 from the dealership. The Next-Generation Mazda 3 hatchback strikes one with its powerful, seductive presence and strong sporty appeal. It is designed to makes one feel like looking at a work of art and not just a car. It has been awarded the maximum five-star rating by Euro NCAP in its latest series of tests. Visit BB Mazda Polokwane on the corner of Rissik and Schoeman streets to view the Next-Generation Mazda 3 or call them on 015 001 0200.